snippet.title: CIVILIZATION VI - E3 2016 Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Watch the behind-closed-doors theater presentation of Civilization VI at E3 2016. Narrated by Sean Bean. SUBSCRIBE for First Looks at other civilizations, leaders, features and tips from the developers of Civilization VI: http://2kgam.es/CivilizationYT

This video walkthrough features actual gameplay that has been edited for time.

FOLLOW US:
